const char *glb_encyclopedia_entry_MOB_CAVETROLL_lines[] =
{
    "When Prakal the Earth Mage was faced with a large band of trolls, he did what seemed reasonable to him at the time.  A few quick casts of petrify would, he thought, result in a nice addition to his museum of curiosities.  Unfortunately, the powerful regenerative nature of trolls prevailed over even Prakal's potent magics.  The trolls were petrified into stone.  Being made of stone didn't make them any more tractable, however.",
    "",
    "Unfortunately for the world at large, Prakal took the better part of valour and ran away.  This left the stone trolls to breed and multiply into what are now properly termed as Cave Trolls."
};

