const char *glb_encyclopedia_entry_MOB_HEADLESS_lines[] =
{
    "The origin of these abominations is unknown.  Well, it is pretty clear that some mad wizard was responsible, but WHICH mad wizard remains in doubt.  Rheo the Book Eater certainly wouldn't have had the foresight to provide them with a crude form of telepathy to compensate for their lack of eyes.  Wpark the Wonderful's fascination with the colour puce rules him out - he'd have surely dyed their hide.  And Treska of the Seven Alphabets?  Her prudish nature would have ensured there was no second generation of headlesses to terrorize the world."
};

