const char *glb_encyclopedia_entry_MOB_LIVINGTREE_lines[] =
{
    "While pedants are quick to point out that all trees are animate - one glance at the destruction wrought by the roots of an oak should settle the skeptical - those who have witnessed a true animate tree feel there is an important distinction between the slow inexorable growth of normal trees and these creatures.  The most obvious difference is that it is a lot harder to run away from an animate tree!",
    "",
    "There is good news for adventurers beset by tree problems.  The animate trees are the result of a spell that hastens the natural life forces.  When the spell's power is used up the trees will revert once again to the pleasant shade-giving plants one is used to."
};

